I obtained the key to a certain room!
\n<Aria>Huh~? ♥ So that's where they were, that person.
\n<Aria>Hey, mister, do you know about madmen? ♥
\n<Detective>!?... Why are you... using that term...

\n<Aria>Hmmm~? Because that person was talking about it,
you know♥ Right now, they're investigating the
phenomenon of madness♥

\n<Aria>Ah~ The chubby one from a little while ago was
different. They were sniffing around various
things a little while before that♥

\n<Aria>\c[24]Could it be that you were friends? ♥
Kyahaha! Sorry~ ♥ I played with them a little and
they ended up breaking♥

\n<Detective>(I heard that several detectives who went to
investigate the scene have become mad... Could it
be that one of them...?)

\n<Detective>As I thought... it seems like you know something.
No, I should say you're involved.

\n<Aria>\c[24]Hehe♥ Well then, if you can make it to
Aria's place, I might just tell you♥
\n<Aria>If you can make it, that is♥

\n<Detective>...I have no choice... I need to subdue him
quickly and hear what those girls have to say as
soon as possible.

\n<Aria>\c[24]Wow, you're doing great♥ So, you're a
detective too, right?♥

\n<Aria>\c[24]I wonder if Aria will be punished because
she's a bad girl?♥ I might get spanked~♥
\n<Detective>...In any case, I need to apply a little pressure.

\n<Aria>\c[24]Eek♥ Scary~♥ I'll be waiting for you with
excitement♥

\n<Aria>\c[24]But, there's still something important to
Aria \c[2]somewhere, so make sure to bring it
properly, okay?♥

\n<Aria>\c[24]That's a surprise♥ Oh, it's not like I'll
complain if you \c[2]use it \c[24]anyway♥ Hehe♥

\n<Detective>...I forgot something... There's still a place
\C[10]that I haven't searched \C[0]yet... I'll
search a little more and find the path to move
forward.
\n<Aria>Huh~? ♥ So it was there, that person, lol.

\n<Aria>Hey, do you know about the madman \C[24], mister?
♥

\n<Aria>Hmmm~? But that person, \C[2]he/she was talking
about it, you know♥ Right now, they're
investigating the phenomenon of madness♥

\n<Aria>Ah~ The chubby one from a little while ago is
different. The one who was sniffing around a
little earlier♥

\n<Aria>\c[24], could it be that you were friends? ♥
Kyahaha! Sorry~ ♥ I played with them a little and
they ended up breaking♥

\n<Detective>(I heard that several detectives who went to
investigate the scene have become mad... Could it
be that one of them...?)

\n<Detective>As I thought... It seems like you know something.
No, I should say you're involved.

\n<Aria>\c[24]Hehe♥ Well then, if you can make it to
Aria's place, I might tell you♥
\n<Aria>If you can make it here, that is♥

\n<Detective>...I have no choice... I need to subdue him
quickly and hear what those girls have to say as
soon as possible.

\n<Aria>\c[24]Wow, you're doing great♥ So, you're a
detective too, right?♥

\n<Aria>\c[24]I wonder if Aria will be punished because
she's been a bad girl?♥ I might get spanked~♥
\n<Detective>...In any case, I need to apply a little pressure.

\n<Aria>\c[24]Eek♥ Scary~♥ I'll be waiting for you with
excitement♥

\n<Aria>\c[24]But, there's still something important to
Aria that should be somewhere, so make sure to
bring it properly, okay?♥
\n<Detective>What?... What kind of thing is that...

\n<Aria>\c[24]That's a surprise♥ Oh, it's not like I'll
complain if you \c[2]use it\c[24], you know♥ Hehe♥

\n<Detective>...I still haven't searched for the forgotten
item... There must be a place I haven't looked
yet.... Let's search a little more and find the
path to move forward.
